The Zondo Commission will continue to hear Eskom related evidence from the former Board Chairperson at Eskom, Zola Tsotsi at 9:30 am Tuesday 8 September 2020. Editor's note: This livestream has ended. You can watch the recording above. JOHANNESBURG - The state capture inquiry will continue to hear Eskom related evidence on Tuesday. Former Eskom board chairperson Zola Tsotsi will be testifying. READ: Load-shedding was always going to be a problem - former Eskom CEO He has previously testified at the commission. Tsotsi resigned as Eskom board chairperson in 2015 after four years at the helm.